      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🚀 How to Use\n\nSend any event to the webhook:\n\ncurl -X POST YOUR_WEBHOOK_URL \\\n-H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n-d '{\n  \"source\": \"stripe\",\n  \"event_type\": \"payment_success\",\n  \"payload\": { \"amount\": 49.99 }\n}'\n\nUse it to log: form submissions, payment\nevents, GitHub webhooks, errors, anything!",
